		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-star"></i>Benefits</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Keep track of current and previous project tasks. </li>
					<li>Set task priorities and status. </li>
					<li>Manage project task due dates. </li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Features</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Create new tasks, bugs, and features</li>
					<li>Set task priorities</li>
					<li>Update task status</li>
					<li>Organize tasks by project. </li>
					<li>Share projects with connections and colleages.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

